muon
------------------------------------------
muon is an implementation of the meson build system in c99 with minimal
dependencies.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libarchive13-3.8.6-1
  libcurl4-8.19.0-1
  libpkgconf7-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  flex-2.6.4-2
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libarchive-devel-3.8.6-1
  libcurl-devel-8.19.0-1
  libpkgconf-devel-2.5.1-1
  meson-1.6.1-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1
  vala-0.56.18-1

Canonical website:
  https://muon.build/

Canonical download:
  https://muon.build/releases/v0.6.0/muon-v0.6.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack muon-0.6.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./muon-0.6.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/muon-0.6.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/muon-0.6.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(muon)
  /usr/bin/muon.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/muon.README
  /usr/share/doc/muon/Apache-2.0.txt
  /usr/share/doc/muon/GPL-3.0-only.txt
  /usr/share/doc/muon/MIT.txt
  /usr/share/doc/muon/Python-2.0.txt
  /usr/share/doc/muon/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/muon/Unlicense.txt
  /usr/share/man/man1/muon.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man3/meson-reference.3.gz
  /usr/share/man/man5/meson.build.5.gz

